## 🛠 Routine for the next BEARDEN session

1. Manually load context (read 3 MANIFESTs + 3 STATUSes + topic-tree index + latest audit)
2. Re-read this STATUS for recent state
3. Verify bot state via `curl http://localhost:<port>/dashboard/state` before any pm2-reload-triggering edit
4. Do the requested work
5. **Before declaring done:** update this STATUS's "Live right now" + "Recently completed" + "Open questions"
6. Append a journal entry + commit
